      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "马超、庞德同上，双起霸。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00002",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "马超"
      ],
      "text": "威镇西凉胆气高，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00003",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "庞德"
      ],
      "text": "白马银枪逞英豪。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00004",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马超"
      ],
      "text": "将军请了！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00005",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庞德"
      ],
      "text": "请了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00006",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马超"
      ],
      "text": "今日父帅升帐，你我两厢伺候！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00007",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庞德"
      ],
      "text": "请！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00008",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四西凉兵引马腾、韩遂同上，同归帐，同坐。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00009",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马超",
        "庞德"
      ],
      "text": "参见（父帅）（元帅）！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00010",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "少礼。两厢伺候！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00011",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马超",
        "庞德"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00012",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "指望靖难力勤王，数万雄师离西凉。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00013",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
