      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "累次攻战师无向，堪恨空劳枉逞强！此际心中怀惆怅，再想良谋保朝堂。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00015",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，你我自起勤王之兵，屯于山口，结内应于三家，统大兵于外镇。不想机关泄露，三户被诛。今有小校来报，那李傕、郭汜二贼，反将三人首级，高悬营前，以壮其威。本欲率兵进攻，怎奈军粮不敷，好生愁闷人也！",
      "text_length": 97
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00016",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "吾已遣将催粮去了，不日即到，以应军用。我与仁兄，分兵两路，夺入山谷，过了此川，李、郭二贼，不难擒也。",
      "text_length": 50
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00017",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "报！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00018",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "报子上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00019",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "粮饷被贼抢，敌势太猖狂！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00020",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "报子进门。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00021",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "报子告进！启二位主帅：并州解来军粮，行至陈仓道口，尽被敌军抢去，奔入深谷去了。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00022",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾",
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "知道了。再探！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00023",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "报子"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00024",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "报子下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00025",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀，敌人久老吾师，又将军粮劫去，事在燃眉，须当早作计较。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00026",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "为今之计，不如暂且退兵。待等秋凉，再起兵讨之，未为晚也。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00027",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "此言甚合吾意。可传令诸将，预备今夜拔营。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00028",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "说得有理。此皆天数当然，等待养成锐气，再整军马，共灭叛逆便了。众将官，就此拔营，回转西凉去者！",
      "text_length": 47
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00029",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众人"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00030",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二纛旗同上，众人同上马。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00031",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "秉正丹心除逆党，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00032",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "怎奈他兵暗隐藏！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00033",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "免战牌高挂营门上，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00034",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "空劳我军受风霜。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00035",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "粮饷不济收兵往，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00036",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "再整雄师灭强梁。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00037",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00038",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四军士、四大铠、张济、樊稠同上。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00039",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "张济"
      ],
      "text": "运筹帷幄意精详，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00040",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "樊稠"
      ],
      "text": "樊笼困鸟怎翱翔。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00041",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张济"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，那马腾、韩遂，必因军粮不接，夜间弃营遁去。俺与将军兵分两路，打从山谷绕出，以劫其军。两下相继而战，料马腾、韩遂，难出我计矣！",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00042",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "樊稠"
      ],
      "text": "兵贵神速。众将官，就此抄路截杀者！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00043",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四军士",
        "四大铠"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00044",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "张济"
      ],
      "text": "分路剿杀休轻放，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00045",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "樊稠"
      ],
      "text": "整顿威风战西羌。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00046",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "张济"
      ],
      "text": "莫教遁去留余障！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00047",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "樊稠"
      ],
      "text": "兵速如风声势扬。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00048",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00049",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四西凉兵、马腾、韩遂同上，二纛旗随上。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00050",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "各整行装收兵将，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00051",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "衔枚息鼓避锋芒。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00052",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "众将官，前面已近大山口。急急趱行，恐有伏兵，截杀不便！",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00053",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四西凉兵"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00054",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内同白",
      "speakers": [
        "四军士",
        "四大铠"
      ],
      "text": "杀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00055",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩遂"
      ],
      "text": "呀，你听喊杀之声渐近。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00056",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马腾"
      ],
      "text": "吾已令庞德、马超断后。我与贤弟前行便了！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00057",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四军士、四大铠引张济、樊稠同上，会阵。四军士、四大铠、樊稠、四西凉兵、韩遂自两边分下。",
      "text_length": 43
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00058",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张济"
      ],
      "text": "马腾哪里走！快快住马，与你比试三合！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03065001_e00059",
      "play_id": "03065001",
      "scene_id": "03065001_s03",
